      <title>先正达寻求 30 亿美元 ESG 贷款，为今年亚洲最大贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/syngenta-seeks-3-billion-esg-loan-asia-s-biggest-this-year</link>
